query:
SELECT temperature::real as "temperature!: f32",
                   humidity::real as "humidity!: f32",
                   pressure::real as "pressure!: f32",
                   soil_moisture::real as "soil_moisture!: f32",
                   water_level::real as "water_level!: f32"
            FROM sensor_data
            ORDER BY created_at DESC
            LIMIT 1
